    <item>
      <title>法国十一月消费者信心意外下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/french-consumer-confidence-drops-unexpectedly-in-november</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国消费者信心 11 月份意外下降，在政府努力争取议会通过预算而不被赶下台之际，这给经济增添了阻力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/french-consumer-confidence-drops-unexpectedly-in-november</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 07:48:25 GMT</pubDate>
